            <h1 class="section-heading">Explore CineFiles</h1>
            <p>
              CineFiles is an ongoing project of the <a href="https://bampfa.org">BAMPFA</a> Film Library and Study Center. This website contains scans of reviews, press kits, film festival and repertory theater programs, articles, and other film ephemera from our extensive library collections.
            </p>
            <p>
              Some documents are restricted due to copyright and require a free <a href="/users/sign_up">account</a> to access. Read about CineFiles accounts, our privacy policy, and more <a href="https://bampfa.org/cinefiles/about/accounts/">here</a>.
            </p>
